ured programming language. One of the reasons for this is having various program control statements. C process the decision making capabilities and supports the statements known as control statements.          
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  C supports 3 types of control statements. Th\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 ey are :
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0     1.  Conditional  control statements.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0     2.  Unconditional control statements.
