\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 ions and net salary by the following table.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 Grade             Basic               HRA         DA         TA        IT         PF
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  A                  <=2000               10%         15%         3%        0         5%
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  A          >2000 & <=5000        15            20             5          3           8
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  A                 >5000                   20            25            8           5          12
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  B                <=3000                  8              10          \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 12           0           4
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  B        >3000 & <=5000         10              12           4            2          8
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  B                >5000                   15              18            5           4         10    
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 
