\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\ul\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 loop: 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0       The process of repeatedly executing a block of statement up to specified number of times is called as loop.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 C supports 3 types of looping statements. They are :
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0           1) while loop
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0         \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0   2) do-while loop
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0           3) for loop
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs24\ul\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 While loop (Entry control loop statement) :
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0   It is a conditional controlled loop statement in C language.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs24\ul\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 Syntax :
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0                  while(test condition)
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0                   \{
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0                           Statements;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0                   \}
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 
       In this loop first the test condition will be evaluated. If it is true, then the statement block will be executed. After the execution of statements, the test condition will be evaluated once again, if it is true then the statem
\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 ent block will be executed once again. This process of repeated execution continued until the test condition becomes false.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs24\ul\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 
