\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af44\afs44 \ltrch\fcs0 \f44\fs28\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44 
        The processor is a program that process the source code before it passes through the compiler. The commands used to control the processor are known as preprocessor directives. 
\par \hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44    These directives are divided into 3 categories.
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-360\li1440\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx1440\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin1440\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af44\afs44 \ltrch\fcs0 \f44\fs28\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44 1.\tab File inclusion d
\hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44 irectives
\par \hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44 2.\tab Macro substitution directives
