\f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  that contains 1\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 00 elements, each element is defined to be of type }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 
\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 struct student}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid11017018\charrsid13244520 .
